          <a
            href={`${phoneNumber}`}
            class="btn btn-primary btn-lg d-lg-none fw-bold"
            ><i class="bi bi-telephone-fill me-2"></i>Call Us For a Quote</a
          >
        </div>
        <div class="d-lg-none">
          <script
            defer
            async
            src="https://cdn.trustindex.io/loader.js?7879b9e328722239bd2655baba4"
          ></script>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="container py-5">
      <script
        defer
        async
        src="https://cdn.trustindex.io/loader.js?970f1f43772a7761fc3694ff98e"
      ></script>
    </div>
    <main class="py-5 bg-light">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="fw-bold text-center mb-4">24 Hour Tyre Service</h1>
        <p class="lead text-center mb-4">
          We know how stressful it can be when you get a flat tyre – that’s why
          we’re here to help! Whether you’re stuck on the side of the road or at
          home, Tyre Emergency is just a phone call away. We’ll come to you, no
          matter the time or place, and fit a new tyre fast, so you can get back
          on the road safely.
        </p>

      </div>
    </main>
    <section class="container py-5">
        <!-- How It Works Section -->
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p class="lead">
            When you're stranded with a flat tyre, we know that <em>speed is key.</em> That’s why we keep the process simple and quick:
        </p>
        <ol class="lead">
            <li><strong>Call Us</strong>: Let us know your tyre size and location, and we’ll be on our way!</li>
            <li><strong>We Arrive</strong>: Our mobile service will be with you in 60 minutes or less – fast and reliable.</li>
            <li><strong>Tyre Fitting</strong>: Our expert technicians will replace your flat tyre quickly and safely.</li>
            <li><strong>Payment</strong>: Choose your preferred payment method – cash or card – and you’re good to go!</li>
        </ol>
    </section>
    
    <section class="bg-dark text-light text-center py-5">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="fs-3 fw-bold">Call Now A Quote</p>
        <a href={`tel:${phoneNumber}`} class="call-btn"
          ><i class="bi bi-telephone-fill me-2"></i> {phoneNumber}</a
        >
      </div>
    </section>
    <CTABar phoneNumber={phoneNumber} />
    <section class="container py-5">
        <!-- How It Works Section -->
        <h2>Areas We Cover</h2>
        <p class="lead">
            Our mobile tyre fitters cover a wide range of the East Midlands, including:
        </p>
        <ol class="lead">
            <li><strong>Nottingham</strong>: Beeston, Hucknall, Arnold, West Bridgford, Stapleford</li>
            <li><strong>Newark</strong>: Balderton, Fernwood, Coddington, Southwell, Winthorpe</li>
            <li><strong>Mansfield</strong>: Ravenshead, Shirebrook, Mansfield Woodhouse, Forest Town, Pleasley</li>
            <li><strong>Worksop</strong>: Carlton-in-Lindrick, Kilton, Shireoaks, Langold, South Worksop</li>
        </ol>
        
    </section>
    <section class="bg-dark text-light text-center py-5">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="fs-3 fw-bold">Call Now A Quote</p>
          <a href={`tel:${phoneNumber}`} class="call-btn"
            ><i class="bi bi-telephone-fill me-2"></i> {phoneNumber}</a
          >
        </div>
      </section>

